    <!-- EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
    <div class="section" id="executive-summary">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon green">üìã</div>
            <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            Talkpush takes AI fairness, accuracy, and transparency seriously. This document provides a comprehensive overview of our safeguards across three critical areas: <strong>bias prevention</strong>, <strong>output accuracy</strong>, and <strong>internal quality controls</strong>. Our approach combines automated real-time monitoring, multi-layered testing before deployment, and continuous improvement loops to ensure that TalkScore AI interviews are fair, reliable, and explainable.
        </p>

        <div class="exec-grid">
            <div class="exec-card bias">
                <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Bias & Fairness</h4>
                <p>9 distinct bias categories are monitored in real-time on every single call. Automated alerts trigger immediate review when any flag is detected.</p>
                <span class="verdict pass">‚úì Real-Time Monitoring Active</span>
            </div>
            <div class="exec-card accuracy">
                <h4>üéØ Accuracy</h4>
                <p>TalkScore uses ML models trained on human examiners' ratings to evaluate 5 language dimensions and soft skills. All outputs validated through rigorous pre-deployment and post-deployment QA.</p>
                <span class="verdict pass">‚úì Validated &amp; Monitored</span>
            </div>
            <div class="exec-card controls">
                <h4>‚öôÔ∏è Internal Controls</h4>
                <p>Every AI agent undergoes rigorous multi-stage QA before deployment, including 100+ automated test calls with diverse candidate profiles. Post-deployment monitoring catches any issues in real-time.</p>
                <span class="verdict pass">‚úì Multi-Layer QA Active</span>
            </div>
        </div>
