        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-icon green">üìÑ</div>
            <h2>Summary</h2>
        </div>
        <p>
            Talkpush's TalkScore AI interview platform is built on a foundation of fairness, accuracy, and transparency:
        </p>
        <ul class="checklist">
            <li><strong>Bias is actively prevented</strong> ‚Äî 9 bias categories monitored in real-time on every call, with pre-deployment testing using 100+ diverse candidate simulations</li>
            <li><strong>Accuracy is built on human expertise</strong> ‚Äî ML models trained on professional human examiner ratings evaluate 5 language dimensions and soft skills independently, ensuring outputs align with expert judgment</li>
            <li><strong>Internal controls are robust and continuous</strong> ‚Äî multi-stage QA before deployment, real-time monitoring after, automated alerts, and systematic improvement loops</li>
            <li><strong>Every decision is explainable</strong> ‚Äî all calls are recorded, transcribed, scored transparently, and fully auditable</li>
            <li><strong>The system improves over time</strong> ‚Äî every detected issue triggers corrections that benefit all future candidates</li>
        </ul>

